STATE
v.
WALKER, Browning & Hernandez. No. 16P05-2. Supreme Court of North Carolina. December 19, 2006. Seth Edwards, District Attorney, for State of NC. Brian Michael Aus, Durham, for Emil E. Browning, Jr. Daniel L. Pollitt, Assistant Appellate Defender, for Jason Christopher Walker. Geoffrey W. Hosford, Wilmington, for Javier A. Hernandez, Jr.

The following order has been entered on the motion filed on the 26th day of August 2005 by Plaintiff for Temporary Stay:

"Motion for Stay Dissolved by order of the Court in conference this the 19th day of December 2006."
